AC_MSG_RESULT([
** Configuration summary for $PKG_NAME $PKG_VERSION $PKG_REL_DATE:

 Compile samba-vscan for Samba      : $SAMBA_VERSION_PRINT
 Compile samba-vscan with sources in: $SAMBA_SOURCE
 Compile samba-vscan backends       : $VSCAN_BACKENDS
